    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. so if the UN is basically just a talking shop that can't actually stop anything, does that mean the whole idea of international law or global cooperation is basically just kind of a myth? like, is the idea of \"global governance\" even a realistic thing or is it just something people pretend works to feel better?",
